# Environment Configuration

## SESSION_PASSWORD
# Required: A strong password for encrypting session cookies
# Generate with: openssl rand -hex 32
SESSION_PASSWORD=your_strong_password_here_32_chars_minimum

## GitHub Webhook Secret
# Required: Secret used to verify webhook signatures from GitHub
# Generate new in GitHub repo settings > Webhooks
GITHUB_WEBHOOK_SECRET=your_webhook_secret_here

## GitHub API (Future Use)
# Optional: Will be used in Phase 2 for AI-powered remediation
GEMINI_API_KEY=your_gemini_api_key_here

## Environment
# Development or Production
NODE_ENV=development
